headline: Super Micro: Likely The Most Hated AI Stock
summary: Super Micro has pulled back to yearly lows due to recent accounting concerns and order upshots despite strong AI server demand. See why SMCI stock is a Strong Buy.

headline: Super Micro Jumps 11%: Turnaround Begins or a Dead Cat Bounce?
summary: Super Micro Computer (NASDAQ:SMCI) was once a Wall Street favorite, riding the artificial intelligence (AI) wave with shares surging nearly 100% in early 2025.
